============Additional application arguments============

-merge_buf_thresold N : Set the travel list thresold for streamed merging.
Example : -merge_buf_thresold 100000
(Which translates to:handle maximum 100K travels per block pass)

-b_silent : Disable logging during runtime profiling session(if enabled)

-perm_size : Set permutation ring buffer size.Default is 32 but the higher the better...
Example : -perm_size 64

